data.name: InvalidRequest
data.value: The request is missing a required parameter, includes an invalid parameter value, includes a parameter more than once, or is otherwise malformed

data.name: UnauthorizedClient
data.value: The client is not authorized to request an access token using this method

data.name: AccessDenied
data.value: The resource owner or authorization server denied the request

data.name: UnsupportedResponseType
data.value: The authorization server does not support obtaining an access token using this method

data.name: InvalidScope
data.value: he requested scope is invalid, unknown, or malformed

data.name: ServerError
data.value: The authorization server encountered an unexpected condition that prevented it from fulfilling the request

data.name: TemporarilyUnavailable
data.value: The authorization server is currently unable to handle the request due to a temporary overloading or maintenance of the server
